    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "#Do This:\n\n**Every app starts with understanding the people who will use it.**\n\nWith your partner, discuss what a user who needs this app might want or need.\n- *What frustrations might they have?*\n- *What would make this app useful for them?*",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/058196490148fcd8886badb844b389ca-Screenshot 2025-10-15 101552.png",
        "key": "undefined-b8e93e67-06ce-4df3-9e14-eac51dfd50ca",
        "layout": "text-bottom-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "# Do This:\n\n**Discuss** with your partner and **record evidence vs. inference** in your activity guide T-Chart.\n- *Example:*\n   - _**Evidence** = Alex uses a phone at lunch_\n   - _**Inference** = Alex needs quick access offline_",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/657a2fb765c52dab5568dfea40197663-Screenshot 2025-10-15 103952.png",
        "key": "undefined-b425644a-5615-4d4f-ae70-21ea56e46dcc",
        "layout": "text-bottom-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "# Use AI to Build Persona Details\n\nAI can help you think through your user's goals, frustrations, and daily context - but **you** stay in charge of what feels realistic.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/154e852b73c4947958b8ce90440a8370-panel3.gif",
        "key": "undefined-71ae662f-45a6-4495-95ca-e38b0f375bc6",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "# Use AI to Help Create a Problem Statement\n\n* Discuss with your partner how this statement connects to Alex’s needs.\n* What makes it focused on a need, not a solution?\n* Then, write your own problem statement in your Activity Guide.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/32721c622e65f70d00622e892e6d8252-Screenshot 2025-10-15 132453.png",
        "key": "undefined-246fb82f-eda2-45ea-b109-3bcd3dea5af8",
        "layout": "text-top-left"
      }
    ]
  },
